## Frontend

- Use tailwind for all CSS styling.
- Use bun for package management.
- User pinia for state management

- Do not fill the components with code that is better suited in a class or composable.

### Frontend Requests

- NEVER under any circumstances use async/await, use promises with then and catch instead.
- ALWAYS use promises with then and catch instead of async/await.
